a:2:{s:7:"content";s:990:"<h1>News / Alerts</h1>
<p>Use the News tool to deliver instructor messages, course information, and other updates. Instantly or schedule then to appear later!  News item should be short and <em>should not</em> contain content.  </p>
<blockquote>
<p>Find the news tool under the <em>course home</em> tab or <em>course tools" then </em>edit course*</p>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li>See news alerts in the news widget on the first page when entering the course in "Course Home" </li>
<li>Receive instant <a href="/grav/grav-skeleton-rtfm-site/d2lbasics/news" title="Notifications">notifications</a> in their email or on their phone when news alerts are posted</li>
<li>Use the <a href="http://www.brightspace.com/products/pulse/" title="Get the Pulse App Here">Pulse app</a> to receive news and calendar notifications</li>
<li>Subscribe to the news feed using <a href="/grav/grav-skeleton-rtfm-site/d2lbasics/news" title="RSS Feeds">RSS Feeds</a> '(see advanced topic)'  </li>
</ul>
